---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Emergence of Cyber-Arachnid Surveillance | T3kluv"
  description="A deep dive into bio-mimetic robotics and decentralized neural networks for urban intelligence gathering."
  currentPath="/articles"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative w-full h-[500px] md:h-[870px] overflow-hidden flex items-end">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface via-surface/40 to-transparent z-10"></div>
    <img
      alt="Cyber-Arachnid"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover grayscale brightness-75"
      src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDiJXIyp2t0MHXOkvA7ZqCS_IkjKUsJNZ-PA8RYxRiZZZWSxXv-AWYgMI56hjcnGi81P38SsMUsKAON_RE3N4rNKUoqH9w2uu1aEHqFqzt70Z_AyPdodo7DXniCfnny1WxWIptCTpk5y4QjYeNPEJqR3jgd1X1MMD1s_AtubJEe9G6IZ6r-OahwEqUbHVx6YjFEfWhaRtm8BjsYWfcBGWonZOKTftrcQLk1LGFKwi7MS0_WhdYYAhvfG5a1_ecuYIrFqlC5gktsxVAR"
    />
    <div class="relative z-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16 md:pb-24 w-full">
      <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-primary-fixed-dim/10 border border-primary-fixed-dim/30 text-primary-fixed-dim font-label text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
        Research Archive // 04.22.24
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-primary leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter mb-8 max-w-5xl">
        The Emergence of Cyber-Arachnid Surveillance
      </h1>
      <div class="data-strip mb-8 w-1/4"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 text-on-surface-variant font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-outline-variant"></span>
          <span>By Elias Vance</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">schedule</span>
          <span>12 Min Read</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Article Content -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16">
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <article class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-10">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light text-on-surface leading-relaxed">
        In the shadowed corners of the Neo-Seoul industrial sector, a new form of observation has taken root. It does not look like a camera, nor does it hum with the familiar static of a drone. It moves with a terrifying, fluid grace—eight articulated limbs navigating the vertical labyrinth of the city with absolute silence.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl font-bold text-primary pt-6">The Architecture of Silence</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-lg">
        Traditional surveillance is static. Even the most advanced satellite imagery or high-altitude UAVs are limited by line-of-sight and environmental interference. The cyber-arachnid, however, utilizes "Sub-Surface Navigation"—a technique where sensors integrated into the chassis read vibration patterns through structural steel and concrete.
      </p>

      <div class="my-16 relative aspect-video bg-surface-container-low overflow-hidden group">
        <img
          alt="Micro-Circuitry"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 grayscale group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
          src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAhvyWW1uhsfRHB8Ym6KegxougdF_bE2zknO-RmRV6TYgqcSc_TSv6tAf08SqQlZLyTEn5h3GHhEzVG56lKgFE4g6PxQK8rGMk0HZtNBADIMHHRj0oK4R_VQQc0tj87KzNUrRO_15-4MuCDqiGpi5Yv50oMgZcuwuFoICEQcg5ewb-vhcK-TjRkpnFjNrw4SHa4Gv5sGd8KWKBp6XM2RbcgJy3MrlopjTUUVKAjTlIKKKHya0Mb749jtUMk1p3lFPbiCrT3kiIos8O-"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-primary-fixed-dim bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-md px-2 py-1">
          Fig 1.2: Integrated Neural Processing Core
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-lg">
        What makes these units particularly formidable is their decentralized intelligence. Unlike a standard remote-piloted craft, these units function as a "Swarm Mind." Data gathered by a single unit in a ventilation shaft is processed across the entire local network, allowing for real-time triangulation of subjects without a centralized server that could be intercepted.
      </p>

      <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-primary-fixed-dim pl-8 py-4 my-12 bg-surface-container-lowest/50 italic">
        <p class="text-2xl font-headline font-medium text-primary leading-snug">
          "We aren't just building robots; we are engineering an ecosystem that watches itself."
        </p>
        <cite class="block mt-4 text-xs font-label uppercase tracking-widest text-on-secondary-container">— Dr. Aris Thorne, Lead Architect</cite>
      </blockquote>

      <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-lg">
        The ethical implications are, predictably, being ignored by the private security conglomerates funding the research. When the observer is indistinguishable from the environment, the concept of a "private space" effectively dissolves into a digital void.
      </p>
    </article>

    <!-- Sidebar -->
    <aside class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-4 bg-surface-container p-6 border border-outline-variant/10">
        <h4 class="font-headline text-xs font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Executive Summary</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          A deep dive into the integration of bio-mimetic robotics and decentralized neural networks for urban intelligence gathering.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 bg-surface-container p-6 border border-outline-variant/10">
        <h4 class="font-headline text-xs font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">Key Subjects</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-surface-container-low text-[10px] text-on-surface tracking-tighter border border-outline-variant/20">BIO-TECH</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-surface-container-low text-[10px] text-on-surface tracking-tighter border border-outline-variant/20">NEURAL NETS</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-surface-container-low text-[10px] text-on-surface tracking-tighter border border-outline-variant/20">SURVEILLANCE</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 bg-surface-container-low p-6 border border-outline-variant/10">
        <h5 class="font-headline text-xs font-bold text-primary-fixed-dim tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Related Articles</h5>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="group cursor-pointer">
            <h6 class="font-headline text-sm font-bold text-on-surface group-hover:text-primary-fixed-dim transition-colors">Post-Human Privacy: The End of the Anonymous City</h6>
          </div>
          <div class="group cursor-pointer pt-4 border-t border-outline-variant/20">
            <h6 class="font-headline text-sm font-bold text-on-surface group-hover:text-primary-fixed-dim transition-colors">Quantum Encryption vs. Swarm Intelligence</h6>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
